{"type": "article", "id": 14821, "title": "香料种在了用餐区，这个餐厅像是个植物王国", "description": "照这个架势下去，除了雇佣一些厨师，还得雇佣个园丁啊。", "date": "2015-09-14T06:16:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4814, "name": "餐厅设计"}, {"id": 228, "name": "以色列"}, {"id": 15929, "name": "植物餐厅"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 295, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164451quj7t9hvS8mifCsF.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t在以色列的 Hod Hasharon ，有一家被植物、香草、鲜花充斥的餐厅，<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/10/the-plants-in-this-restaurant-are-herbs-that-the-chef-uses-to-cook-with/\" target=\"_blank\">叫作 Segev Kitchen Garden </a>，是由建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://www.yarontal.com/\">Studio Yaron Tal</a> 设计的。在设计的过程中，建筑师给植物预留了许多空间，他们把香草和植物种在了餐厅里，这些植物既是装饰，也是食材。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164445162zjSiNna4twpeP.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"742\" title=\"餐厅里层林掩映\" alt=\"餐厅里层林掩映\" data-ratio=\"1.159375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>餐厅里层林掩映</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164445mWoeNL8Dvrc69TQb.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"261\" title=\"远景\" alt=\"远景\" data-ratio=\"0.4078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>远景。植物被放在地上、搁在架子上，它们还爬满了房梁</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021644462vRsXHrYgTkuWG3L.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"264\" title=\"另一个角度\" alt=\"另一个角度\" data-ratio=\"0.4125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另一个角度</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164447lzpuA7VBtnG14mWr.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"284\" title=\"餐厅里的大树\" alt=\"餐厅里的大树\" data-ratio=\"0.44375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>餐厅里的大树</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164447zWHoEb7IrPKSvtu5.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"768\" title=\"植物遮挡住了大部分光线，恐怕在白天也要开灯\" alt=\"植物遮挡住了大部分光线，恐怕在白天也要开灯\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>植物遮挡住了大部分光线，在白天恐怕也要开灯</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021644489zSZeP2oktCidK75.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"727\" title=\"多人用餐区域\" alt=\"多人用餐区域\" data-ratio=\"1.1359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>多人用餐区域</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164448VEdMj1UH3aWC5lJz.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"890\" title=\"独特的吊灯\" alt=\"独特的吊灯\" data-ratio=\"1.390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>独特的吊灯</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216444992wDERtVzGnasgW7.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"792\" title=\"一些古旧的装饰\" alt=\"一些古旧的装饰\" data-ratio=\"1.2375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>一些古旧的装饰</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164449J0c5rAsoqTDgLnFi.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"648\" title=\"老式的洗手龙头\" alt=\"老式的洗手龙头\" data-ratio=\"1.0125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>老式的洗手龙头</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>除了设计餐饮空间外，该建筑事务所还完成了不少其他类型的室内设计。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164450IdBtlQkzf4UZhpsv.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"370\" title=\"办公空间设计\" alt=\"办公空间设计\" data-ratio=\"0.578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>办公空间设计</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164450e72sfj4SElw6yDo3.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"370\" title=\"餐厅设计\" alt=\"餐厅设计\" data-ratio=\"0.578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>餐厅设计</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164451eRbaS3ylgCP6YxNH.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"370\" title=\"餐厅设计\" alt=\"餐厅设计\" data-ratio=\"0.578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>餐厅设计</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span><em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/10/the-plants-in-this-restaurant-are-herbs-that-the-chef-uses-to-cook-with/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>contemporist</em><em></em></a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}